  "6 seconds": "",
  "48 seconds": "",
  "16 seconds": "",
  "Set h = 0: -16t^2 + 48t = 0, factor: -16t(t - 3) = 0. So t = 0 (launch) or t = 3 (landing). The ball hits the ground at 3 seconds.": "",
